title: OCVarsity Gridiron starts getting you ready for Week 7
text:
OCVarsity Gridiron starts getting you ready for Week 7 October 12, 2015 11:42 PM | Print Story | E-Mail Story OCVARSITY.COM 
OCVarsity's Gridiron Crew - Steve Fryer, Dan Albano and Jonathan Khamis - start getting you ready for the Week 7 football games. 
First, they wrap up Week 6 by announcing the players of the week. Then they start looking ahead at the top matchups in Week 7, which include Mater Dei vs. St. John Bosco, Tesoro vs. Mission Viejo and Buena Park vs. La Habra. 
Video by Jonathan Khamis, OCVarsity.com.
